name: Elsa
aboutCharacter: Elsa is the perfect mythic character – magical and larger than life. Grateful her kingdom now accepts her, she works hard to be a good queen. But deep down she can’t help but wonder why she was born with powers.

name: Anna
aboutCharacter: Anna is the perfect fairytale character; unflappable, she is the forever optimist. Anna is fine as long as she has her family, Arendelle is safe, and she never has to be alone again.

name: Kristoff
aboutCharacter: A rugged mountain man and ice harvester by trade, Kristoff was a bit of a loner with his reindeer pal, Sven, until he met Anna. As Arendelle’s official Ice Master and Deliverer, Kristoff has found love with Anna and his new family: Elsa, Olaf and Sven.

name: Olaf
aboutCharacter: Created from Elsa’s magical powers, Olaf is by far the friendliest snowman in Arendelle. He is innocent, outgoing and loves all things summer. Olaf may be a bit naive, but his sincerity and good-natured temperament make him a true friend to Anna and Elsa.

name: Duke of Weselton
aboutCharacter: What the Duke of Weselton lacks in stature, he makes up for in arrogance and showboating.

name: Hans
aboutCharacter: Hans is a handsome royal from a neighboring kingdom who comes to Arendelle for Elsa's coronation.

name: Oaken
aboutCharacter: Oaken runs Wandering Oaken's Trading Post and Sauna.

name: Marshmallow
aboutCharacter: Marshmallow is an enormous icy snowman born from Elsa's powers.

name: Snowgies
aboutCharacter: Snowgies are little snowmen Elsa unwittingly creates every time she sneezes—and she sneezes a lot.

name: Sven
aboutCharacter: A reindeer with the heart of a Labrador, Sven is Kristoff's loyal friend, sleigh-puller and conscience.
